      "text": "The ^#orange;Tricorder^reset; can help you ^orange;equip^reset; and ^orange;refuel^reset; your mech. Fuel is important, so keep your mech topped up. Press the corresponding buttons on the tricorder after this mission to check it out. ^#Red;(If you see 'unauthorized user' restart the mission.)",
