      "text": "Please be aware of your mech's ^#bf2fe2;fuel^white; and ^#1d8e25;health^white; reserves, visualised respectively as the ^green;colored bars you can see above your vehicle^reset;. The ^#bf2fe2;fuel^white; will deplete over time and the ^#1d8e25;health^white; bar will deplete when the mech takes damage.",
